  "body": "## What's Changed\n* Resolve go compiler regression by @williammartin in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8716\n* bug: fixed the msg returned for patching a repo variable by @dean-tate in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8715\n* Fix regression around commas in commit titles during `pr create` by @williammartin in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8768\n* feat: Add `ref` option to `gh cache list` by @toshimaru in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8711\n* Make comments in the default config file more informative by @bartekpacia in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8756\n* Link Project to Repository or Team Command by @benebsiny in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8595\n* Clarify helptext for search prs regarding archived repos by @stuart-leitch in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8738\n* Simplify install command for Debian & Ubuntu by @hongquan in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8693\n* Support `project view --web` with TTY by @harveysanders in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8773\n* Bump cli/go-gh v2.6.0 for tenant using GH_TOKEN by @andyfeller in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8787\n\n## New Contributors\n* @dean-tate made their first contribution in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8715\n* @bartekpacia made their first contribution in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8756\n* @stuart-leitch made their first contribution in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8738\n* @hongquan made their first contribution in https://github.com/cli/cli/pull/8693\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/cli/cli/compare/v2.44.1...v2.45.0",
